# {{ill|Take-Mikagu-tsuchi-no-O|ja|建御雷之男神}}, also known as {{ill|Takefutsu|ja|建布都神}} or {{ill|Toyo-futsu|ja|豊布都神}}
#: The gods above were born from the blood that fell from the blade of the sword.
# {{ill|Kura-Okami|ja|闇淤加美神}}
